          "justification": "The paper explicitly states that the operational version (RDBS-OWL) was used to automatically instantiate the ontology from a real database sample, which constitutes direct implementation and use of the model to create an artifact (an RDF dump). The use of the model to instantiate real-world database structures and enable tasks like migration and publishing confirms its role as an instrument for intervention."
